## pinctrl-0

A list of phandles referring to pin configuration nodes, one per state. `pinctrl-0` is the default (active) state.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
uart7: serial@880000 {
    pinctrl-names = "default", "sleep";
    pinctrl-0 = <&qup_uart7_default>;
    pinctrl-1 = <&qup_uart7_sleep>;
};
```
